    Paralysis went with Quickstrike. He would help the Subcommander with 
whatever he needed. As for Aracnia, the idea of using Rattrap as bait was 
appealing. 
    "Quickstrike, You and Paralysis remian here and prepare the selfdestruct 
mechanism. The rest of us are departing to Kitkats." She said, looking into 
his optics.

    Megatron looked over the radar. For some reason, the Allience ship was on 
the move.....that could be a problem. "General Commander Kitkat," Megatron 
said, because after all she was leading the battle, "Where exactly is Zardus 
going?"
